{"_path":"/blog/2-my-vscode-setup","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"My VSCode Setup | Blog","description":"Explore my minimalist VSCode setup featuring the Minimal Mist theme and settings for a clean, distraction-free coding environment.","headline":"My VSCode Setup","date":"2024-07-17T12:00:00","author":"Muhammad Ubaid Raza","authorUrl":"https://mubaidr.js.org/","socialImage":{"src":"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-light.png","mime":"webp","alt":"Workplace Screenshot","width":1200,"height":630},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"my-vscode-setup"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My VSCode Setup"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hello, fellow developers! I’m Muhammad Ubaid Raza, and I want to share my latest VSCode setup with you. I've crafted this environment to be as minimalist and distraction-free as possible, and I call it Minimal Mist. This theme and setup have greatly enhanced my coding experience, and I hope it can do the same for you."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"features-of-minimal-mist"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Features of Minimal Mist"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"subtle-background"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Subtle Background"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I chose a soft and soothing background color "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#f6f5f0"}]},{"type":"text","value":". This subtle hue reduces eye strain and creates a calm coding environment, perfect for long coding sessions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"shadow-free-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shadow-Free Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In my quest for a cleaner interface, I disabled shadows. This makes the interface feel lighter and less cluttered, allowing me to focus more on my code."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"streamlined-borders"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Streamlined Borders"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Borders can often add unnecessary visual noise, so I simplified, minimized, or removed them. This provides a clean and focused workspace that helps keep distractions at bay."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"clean-look"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Clean Look"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Overall, the goal is a refined, distraction-free interface that lets me concentrate on what matters most - the code."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"unified-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unified Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The dark theme maintains the same streamlined, shadow-free design and simplified borders for a cohesive look."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Minimal Mist, both in light and dark variants, is perfect for developers who value a clean, minimalist aesthetic."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"preview"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Preview"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Here’s a preview of what you can expect:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"typescript"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Typescript"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"Typescript Light","src":"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-light.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"my-vscode-settings"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My VsCode Settings"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To further enhance the workspace setup, I use the following settings to reduce clutter and make my workspace even more minimal without sacrificing any functionality. You can add these settings to your "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"settings.json"}]},{"type":"text","value":" file in VSCode to achieve the same look as in the screenshots above:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":["language-jsonc"],"code":"\"editor.renderLineHighlight\": \"none\",\n\"editor.scrollbar.vertical\": \"hidden\",\n\"window.commandCenter\": false,\n\"window.menuBarVisibility\": \"compact\",\n\"window.titleBarStyle\": \"custom\",\n\"workbench.editor.tabActionCloseVisibility\": false,\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizing\": \"fixed\",\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizingFixedMaxWidth\": 240,\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizingFixedMinWidth\": 180,\n\"workbench.sideBar.location\": \"right\",\n\"workbench.statusBar.visible\": false,\n\"workbench.tree.indent\": 22,\n\"workbench.tree.renderIndentGuides\": \"none\",\n","language":"jsonc","meta":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"editor.renderLineHighlight\": \"none\",\n\"editor.scrollbar.vertical\": \"hidden\",\n\"window.commandCenter\": false,\n\"window.menuBarVisibility\": \"compact\",\n\"window.titleBarStyle\": \"custom\",\n\"workbench.editor.tabActionCloseVisibility\": false,\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizing\": \"fixed\",\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizingFixedMaxWidth\": 240,\n\"workbench.editor.tabSizingFixedMinWidth\": 180,\n\"workbench.sideBar.location\": \"right\",\n\"workbench.statusBar.visible\": false,\n\"workbench.tree.indent\": 22,\n\"workbench.tree.renderIndentGuides\": \"none\",\n"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"features-of-minimal-mist","depth":2,"text":"Features of Minimal Mist","children":[{"id":"subtle-background","depth":3,"text":"Subtle Background"},{"id":"shadow-free-design","depth":3,"text":"Shadow-Free Design"},{"id":"streamlined-borders","depth":3,"text":"Streamlined Borders"},{"id":"clean-look","depth":3,"text":"Clean Look"},{"id":"unified-design","depth":3,"text":"Unified Design"}]},{"id":"preview","depth":2,"text":"Preview"},{"id":"my-vscode-settings","depth":2,"text":"My VsCode Settings"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:2-my-vscode-setup.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/2-my-vscode-setup.md","_stem":"blog/2-my-vscode-setup","_extension":"md"}